\p
\v 7 After YahwehВҰ242946 had said that to Iyyov, \add *he\add* told ElifazВҰ242958 (from TemanВҰ242959), вҖңI'm angry withВҰ242963 you and your two friendsВҰ242964, because what you all said about me wasn't right, like what Iyyov \add said\add*.
\v 8 \add SoВҰ242973\add* now get seven bullsВҰ242979 and seven rams and go to my servant Iyyov and offer \add <them\add* as a burntВҰ242989 offeringВҰ242989 for yourselvesВҰ242990. ThenВҰ242973 my servant Iyyov will pray for you all. \add вүҲI'llВҰ242999 do what he asks and\add* not deal with you like your foolishness \add deserves\add*, because you all didn'tВҰ243000 speak accurately about me like Iyyov did.вҖқ
\p
\v 9 \add SoВҰ243012\add* ElifazВҰ243013 (from TemanВҰ243014) and BildadВҰ243015 (from Shuah) and Zofar (from NaamahВҰ243018) wentВҰ243012 and did what Yahweh had told them, and Yahweh acceptedВҰ243024 Iyyov's \add prayer\add*.
